{"tid":1618191,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"普京：俄協助中國建立導彈攻擊警告系統 大大提高中國防衛能力","createTime":"2019-10-04T04:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T05:45:38.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0165c9369b9f9594bc2c770f64bdd116d0c12b87","tid":1618191,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191004/large/1570126655_ef02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191004%2Flarge%2F1570126655_ef02.jpg&h=4acae889&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n普京在索契(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯總統普京周四說，俄羅斯正協助中國建立導彈攻擊警告系統，此系統目前只有俄羅斯和美國擁有。<br />\n<br />\n他在俄羅斯度假城市索契(Sochi)出席國際政治會議時說：「這是一件認真的事，將大大提高中國的防衛能力。」<br />\n<br />\n普京的聲明標誌中俄兩個前共產敵對大國進一步加強國防合作，政治與軍事聯繫日益緊密。<br />\n<br />\n導彈攻擊警告系統涉及一系列地面雷達與太空衛星，可及早察覺洲際彈道導彈來襲。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/美聯社<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191004/60114954\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191004%2F60114954&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3vilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=d73754b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191004%2F60114954&h=28eb0487\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191004/60114954</a>"},{"pid":"7c9dcf7f0ae6732a1cca46ac06e42476b85fa5e9","tid":1618191,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:47:22.000Z","msg":"習弟： 今鋪又幾錢呀？ 京哥"},{"pid":"0968a0257275a75c3c54bb2c63e87d67c06223fc","tid":1618191,"uid":301152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:50:17.000Z","msg":"隔岸觀中國起火又賺到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f5fe06e240ac6025c635394c1b43f10c6e03871","tid":1618191,"uid":109923,"like":0